{"tid":516190,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本貼心「硬幣對照表」　網友：把外國人當白痴","createTime":"2018-01-01T07:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T07:49:57.000Z","uid":56533,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"227f01f1811c386edc168946bea09fc74a7f7f8b","tid":516190,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T07:22:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180101/640_62a6a6780e1421e9726507d13d49665b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180101%2F640_62a6a6780e1421e9726507d13d49665b.jpg&h=bed63b11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本自動販賣機超貼心的「硬幣比對表」，卻讓不少網友笑「把外國人當白痴？」<br />\n<br />\n去過日本的都知道，日本街上到處都是自動販賣機，已成為台灣旅客必朝聖的特色之一，最近有日本網友發現，自動販賣機上竟出現專為外國人做的「日圓硬幣金額對照表」，上面有中、英、韓文翻譯，圖中很明確指出，硬幣應該要怎麼投，例如160元的飲料要拿出1個1百塊銅板、1個50塊銅板以及10塊銅板，還貼心提醒外國客不要忘記拿找來的錢幣，網友將照片上傳至推特上，引發其他網友熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n有網友認為這完全發揮日本人「盡力服務」的精神，但也有很多網友認為「這根本把外國人當白痴」，有網友吐槽「阿拉伯數字是共通語言吧？」「連硬幣數字都分不清楚的人不應該出國」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20180101/1270047\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20180101%2F1270047&d=zz9N3OG7jFSyxGF8qp4RDy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ff1fba5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20180101%2F1270047&h=af7237d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20180101/1270047</a>"},{"pid":"908158e17b0f8c19f6c4ea1d77ca52452e5c3dbc","tid":516190,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T07:24:50.000Z","msg":"係咪有遊客搏大霧入其他硬幣呀？"},{"pid":"0129e1e77af426be5e24d65a9208e4e461e4ca57","tid":516190,"uid":2333,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T07:28:06.000Z","msg":"台灣旅客朝聖地點<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台豬真係無改錯名"},{"pid":"bc0788050d85caaf966a5ffead464d143642eeff","tid":516190,"uid":74933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T07:28:33.000Z","msg":"有鬼佬比兩毫以為兩蚊添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢擺係度 又冇阻人 又冇煩到你 有咩問題"},{"pid":"c3399861ccdeb5ce605ea0bc06b2093def00218c","tid":516190,"uid":14191,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T07:29:36.000Z","msg":"「連硬幣數字都分不清楚的人不應該出國」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1189c434e3fc64c79b46faea7a09d0b6f9052909","tid":516190,"uid":2998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T07:36:34.000Z","msg":"成日摷銀包個時撈亂100yen同50yen，仲有10yen同5yen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17174bf4f37a185459a6136f88021c252dd2e0ed","tid":516190,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T07:39:03.000Z","msg":"而家日本好多機係一渣神沙放入去, 再扣好數, 找錢<br />\n<br />\n次次D 1~10 YEN 都係咁用晒, 褲袋一渣放入去, 加幾張1000yen <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf1ab1c3b7807621674adc6b7e28a0c2cd2e712","tid":516190,"uid":126221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T07:44:29.000Z","msg":"個人意見：<br />\n<br />\n關乜野事，根本日本人自己都習慣放 d 咁 on9 既野出黎。<br />\n你睇下香港 bread papa 都有張對照表，1 到 10 個泡芙賣幾錢。<br />\n望真 d ，原來一毫子都無減，咁樣其實篤機就知啦。<br />\n呢 d 咁 on9 既野都特登整個表出黎，只能夠講聲佩服。<br />\n<br />\n唔好下下都咁妄想被害症啦好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7fdfe6129f6ad28a4d11a752ee10de99ecf44f","tid":516190,"uid":59140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T07:46:37.000Z","msg":"其實五円係無阿拉伯數字嘅"},{"pid":"0964436dd66aa053b4c701b63eef73636ee47384","tid":516190,"uid":4525,"like":0,"disl